 <span data-ttu-id="2bdc7-149">Пример использования этого свойства см. в <xref:System.Xml.XmlUrlResolver.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bdc7-149">See <xref:System.Xml.XmlUrlResolver.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for an example that uses this property.</span></span>
